HEADWORD: Choker
<hw>Chok"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, chokes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A stiff wide cravat; a stock.</def>
